Defition   : OPT_WHIMPY

Defined in : #include <options.h>

Usage      : player->query_option(OPT_WHIMPY)

Description: Selects the percentage of hurt when the player wants to whimp
             from combat.

Values     : Range: 0-99
              0 - Be brave, never flee.
             99 - Be most whimpy and flee quickly.
